' ]

-----EXAMPLE 5316------
CONTEXT =  [ " it 's hard to be optimistic about things with the way the economy 's headed ... the trade deficit is getting larger , consumption 's down , i really think we 're headed for a recession . " , " the economy has been stagnant for a while now . we 've been in a recessive state for several months already . what worries me the most is the trade deficit . i think the government should do more to encourage exports . " , ' increasing exports would weaken the currency . i think the main point is economic growth . we need more jobs . factories have outsourced and moved many jobs to foreign countries . the result is an increase in unemployment in our own country , lower consumption , lower production , and an overall feeble economy . if more people are working , it will give the economy a boost .
